data.description: With 4 bedrooms and 2.1 baths, this home offers plenty of room! The beautiful porch adds to the charm of this brick bungalow. The flexible floor plan includes 2 main level bedrooms and one each on the upper and lower levels. Enjoy the convenience of two kitchens - one on the main level and the other on the lower level. The large deck and yard are perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. The property also includes a side drive and a detached 2-car garage. Recently updated, this house is move-in ready. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home sweet home!
